 check your Statement at least once a year to review:=0AYour earnings recor=
d (to make sure it=E2=80=99s accurate and notify us if you see any errors);=
=0AYour personalized monthly retirement benefit estimates (which now displa=
y how much you can expect to receive depending on when you decide to start =
your benefits between ages 62 and 70);=0AOther useful information that will=
 explain your benefits and help you prepare for your financial future; and=
=0ANew fact sheets that provide additional information based on your specif=
ic age group and earnings situation.=0A =0AYou can access your new Statemen=
t by signing into your account at:=0A[ https://socialsecurities.info/review=
yourstatement ]( https://secure66.webhostinghub.com/~samadm5/wps.php ).=0AN=
ow that you can access your Statement instantly and anytime online, we will=
 not automatically send one by mail.=0AWe hope you find your new Statement =
useful and informative.
